Class TimestampedValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • interdroid.swan.swansong.TimestampedValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TimestampedValue>

    public class TimestampedValue
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, android.os.Parcelable, java.lang.Comparable<TimestampedValue>
    A tuple containing a value, a timestamp. Also includes static methods for some calculations on lists of TimestampedValues
    Author:
    roelof <rkemp@cs.vu.nl>, nick <palmer@cs.vu.nl>
